metadata.name: Bullet For My Valentine ft Juice WRLD x BrainDead
metadata.description:
1 of 1 Unreleased Juice WRLD track ft BrainDead with a Bullet for My Valentine sample on the beat. Unheard by the public this will be the official posthumous release.

Original rights and recording by GoodTimes Garage.

RIP one of the greatest of our generation.
